ontent/uploads/2024/07/2024_tenaciousd_donaldtrump_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/2024_tenaciousd_donaldtrump_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/2024_tenaciousd_donaldtrump_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/2024_tenaciousd_donaldtrump_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/2024_tenaciousd_donaldtrump_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>在参议员拉尔夫·巴贝特 (Ralph Babet) 在发表有关<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/donald-trump">唐纳德·特朗普</a>的言论后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/australian-senator-calls-for-tenacious-ds-deportation-after-remarks-on-trumps-assassination-attempt-3775285">呼吁将他们驱逐出境后，</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tenacious-d">Tenacious D</a>推迟了今晚（7 月 16 日）在澳大利亚的演出。</p><p>周日（7 月 14 日）在悉尼演出时，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jack-black">杰克·布莱克 (Jack Black)</a>向他的乐队成员凯尔·加斯 (Kyle Gass) 唱了一首《生日快乐》，然后请他许愿。加斯与观众分享了他的愿望，并说道：“下次不要错过<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/donald-trump">特朗普</a>。”</p><p>此番言论指的是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/entertainment-world-reacts-to-shooting-at-donald-trump-rally-3774722">周末一次集会上针对特朗普的刺杀行动未遂</a>，当时一名枪手向前总统开枪，但只擦伤了特朗普的耳朵，并夺走了一名集会人员的生命。</p><p>今天，参议员巴贝特发出一封信，呼吁立即将两人驱逐出澳大利亚。从那时起，乐队取消了今晚在纽卡斯尔的演出。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C9eJbqbs0QZ/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div