格拉斯哥“威利旺卡”活动转变为爱丁堡边缘艺术表演，由 1971 年原版电影演员表演https://www.nme.com/news/film/glasgow-willy-wonka-event-turned-into-edinburgh-fringe-show-with-original-1971-film-actors-3775343?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=格拉斯哥威利旺卡事件变成了爱丁堡边缘艺术节与 1971 年原片演员一起表演Elizabeth AubreyTue, 16 Jul 2024 10:29:10 +0000 Film NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3775343 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Gene-Wilder-in-Willy-Wonka-CREDIT_-hoto-by-Silver-Screen-Collection_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="《威利·旺卡和巧克力工厂》中的吉恩·怀尔德" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Gene-Wilder-in-Willy-Wonka-CREDIT_-hoto-by-Silver-Screen-Collection_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Gene-Wilder-in-Willy-Wonka-CREDIT_-hoto-by-Silver-Screen-Collection_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Gene-Wilder-in-Willy-Wonka-CREDIT_-hoto-by-Silver-Screen-Collection_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Gene-Wilder-in-Willy-Wonka-CREDIT_-hoto-by-Silver-Screen-Collection_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Gene-Wilder-in-Willy-Wonka-CREDIT_-hoto-by-Silver-Screen-Collection_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Gene-Wilder-in-Willy-Wonka-CREDIT_-hoto-by-Silver-Screen-Collection_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>该展览将于今年八月在爱丁堡举行</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/glasgow-willy-wonka-event-turned-into-edinburgh-fringe-show-with-original-1971-film-actors-3775343">格拉斯哥“威利旺卡”活动后的活动变成了爱丁堡边缘艺术节，1971 年的电影演员</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Gene-Wilder-in-Willy-Wonka-CREDIT_-hoto-by-Silver-Screen-Collection_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="《威利·旺卡和巧克力工厂》中的吉恩·怀尔德" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Gene-Wilder-in-Willy-Wonka-CREDIT_-hoto-by-Silver-Screen-Collection_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Gene-Wilder-in-Willy-Wonka-CREDIT_-hoto-by-Silver-Screen-Collection_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Gene-Wilder-in-Willy-Wonka-CREDIT_-hoto-by-Silver-Screen-Collection_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Gene-Wilder-in-Willy-Wonka-CREDIT_-hoto-by-Silver-Screen-Collection_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Gene-Wilder-in-Willy-Wonka-CREDIT_-hoto-by-Silver-Screen-Collection_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Gene-Wilder-in-Willy-Wonka-CREDIT_-hoto-by-Silver-Screen-Collection_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>今年早些时候在格拉斯哥举办的不幸的<i>《威利·旺卡》</i>儿童活动将变成爱丁堡边缘艺术表演，1971 年电影中的两位原班演员也将出席。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/wonka-review-timothee-chalamet-3553138">《旺卡》评论：蒂莫西·查拉梅 (Timothée Chalamet) 在充满乐趣的节日盛宴中闪闪发光</a></strong></li></ul><p>今年早些时候，根据罗尔德·达尔的<i>《威利旺克斯和巧克力工厂》</i>一书和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/timothee-chalamet">蒂莫西·查拉梅的</a>电影<i>《旺卡</i>》改编的儿童体验活动在收到数十起家长投诉后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/flop-willy-wonka-experience-in-glasgow-goes-viral-for-being-so-terrible-3593684">迅速走红</a>。</p><p>这个看似身临其境的<i>旺卡</i>主题景点，在使用廉价道具、服装和人工智能生成的脚本被关在废弃仓库后，令许多格拉斯哥公众感到失望。</p><p>在收到数十起愤怒家长的投诉后，这场每张门票 35 英镑的活动很快被关闭，其中许多人要求退款并报了警。</p><p>现在，在 1971 年吉恩·怀尔德主演的电影中分别扮演维鲁卡·索尔特和迈克·蒂维的朱莉·道恩·科尔和帕丽斯·塞曼将在爱丁堡艺术节上共同讲述一场根据这场灾难改编的新节目。</p><p><i>威利的《糖果奇观：音乐戏仿》</i>也将看到一些参与格拉斯哥原创活动的人也将参加，其中包括科斯蒂·帕特森(Kirsty Paterson)，她因饰演悲伤的奥姆帕·卢姆帕(Oompa Loompa)的照片而走红。组织者还承诺将会有一些额外的“惊喜”，导致人们猜测参与原始活动的其他一些演员也会参加。</p><p>该剧由美国制片人理查德·克拉夫特 (Richard Kraft) 创作，安迪·菲克曼 (Andy Fickman) 执导，将于 8 月 9 日至 26 日在 Pleasance King Dome 上演。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C9cgDiipY1a/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.244,65.022 564.756,66